::GoldenEye:;

She sat there wide eyed for a moment.  He kissed her cheek.  That 
left her stunned for a moment.  No bot had ever done that before to 
her and it suprized her.  "G..Good night."

She watches him settle down in the grove.  She looked back up at the 
stars and smiled.  Life was good, she thought.



In the morning, she rose with the first rays of sun hitting the 
trees.  She stretched and yawned.  She looked over at Dollen to see 
if he was still sleeping or not.
